Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.86,0:00:08.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I heard that Graham's comet\Nwill soon be visible!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.63,0:00:10.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.64,0:00:13.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I know Halley's comet,\Nbut not this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.71,0:00:18.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's the comet that passes\Nclose to Earth every 50 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.32,0:00:20.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.69,0:00:24.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's this Thursday\Nwhen it'll pass by Earth again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.61,0:00:28.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,How wonderful!\NThis Thursday, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.88,0:00:31.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,How romantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:39.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But you can't see it with the naked\Neye. You have to go to an observatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.17,0:00:44.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What would happen\Nif a comet crashed into Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.05,0:00:47.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I guess we'd all be blown to bits.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:52.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Then what will you do, Ryoko?\N-Get my important things and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.60,0:00:54.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-To where?\N-Your important things?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.17,0:00:58.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Let me think...\N-Important things, she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.91,0:01:02.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-My parents, for sure!\N-Mine's my favorite fishing pole.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.92,0:01:07.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,My pillow! I can't sleep without it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.37,0:01:15.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-You guys are a lost cause.\N-What about you, Sawatari?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.99,0:01:20.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Let's run to the end of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.30,0:01:27.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.41,0:01:33.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,A COMET APPROACHES!\NTHE EARTH'S FINAL NIGHT??
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.06,0:01:35.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're all idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.76,0:01:40.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,A comet never leaves its orbit,\Nso it'll never crash into Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:44.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I said "suppose"!\NDon't call me an idiot, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.78,0:01:46.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You want a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.92,0:01:52.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,So that's it! You don't have anything\Nimportant to take, so you're mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.60,0:01:56.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What? You're wrong!\NI do too have something precious!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.14,0:01:59.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Then tell us!\N-You really want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.18,0:02:05.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Are you two friends or enemies?\NMake up your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.74,0:02:13.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Who wants to be friends with him?\N-Same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:21.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Advertise your product or brand here\Ncontact www.OpenSubtitles.org today
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:31.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,He didn't have time to tell me\Nwhat his important thing was.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.62,0:02:34.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Make up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.66,0:02:37.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm not in love with her or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:41.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I just don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:46.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.09,0:02:51.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We must let the American people\Nknow to prevent a tragedy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:54.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But that will only cause a panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.04,0:02:58.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-You're saying to keep quiet?\N-We only have a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:00.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.59,0:03:04.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.59,0:03:05.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:08.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's too soon to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:13.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Mom, where's my snack?\N-There should be something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.51,0:03:15.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:21.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Gosh! What are they watching anyway,\Nall cuddled up during the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.57,0:03:26.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,COMET COLLIDES!\NTHE LAST NIGHT ON EARTH: 1953 USA
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.08,0:03:44.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.25,0:03:48.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It sure did. This was the movie\Nwe saw on our first date.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.76,0:03:51.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Genichiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.90,0:03:54.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Eimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:02.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll go change.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:06.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This is so embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:14.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:18.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:23.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's an incident that\Noccurred about an hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:25.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm first!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:29.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! You mustn't run around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:32.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.89,0:04:37.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're in the choir, aren't you?\NWhat's the big hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.47,0:04:38.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.18,0:04:44.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Graham's comet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.65,0:04:48.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Sister.\NWe have to see that comet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.66,0:04:50.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Akio's going to move away soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:55.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's why we all decided\Nto go see the comet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.34,0:04:58.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-You can't see it with your naked eye.\N-I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.91,0:05:04.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,So I went to the observatory and asked\Nif we could use the telescope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.09,0:05:07.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,At first they agreed, but then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:13.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,No one's told me anything about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:16.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But I talked to\Nthe director last week!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.59,0:05:21.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Last week? That director was\Ntransferred to another observatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:22.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:26.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Then let us talk to the new director!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:30.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,He's a busy man.\NYou're disrupting our work. Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.78,0:05:32.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Oh, my.\N-It's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.69,0:05:38.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We were looking forward to it.\NSo we came to pray for God's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.63,0:05:41.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,So we can get to see the comet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.69,0:05:49.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there some other way, Seira?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.73,0:05:54.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You can only see it with an\Nobservatory's astronomical telescope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:56.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.18,0:06:01.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Let St. Tail handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:11.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It looks like that Sawatari's\Nreally serious about Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.34,0:06:16.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what got into him. He was\Nnever interested in girls before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.72,0:06:20.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-What do you think, Asuka?\N-How would I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:22.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What a grouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.13,0:06:26.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Who cares?\N-Hey! The enemy is approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.51,0:06:29.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.35,0:06:32.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What--?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.79,0:06:35.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.41,0:06:46.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Rotten kids! How dare you\Nattack an innocent passerby?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.79,0:06:52.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Adults are all liars!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:03.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Asuka, looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:05.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You can't hit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:09.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Great strategy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:17.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,"Dear Mr. Detective:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.42,0:07:22.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I will steal Graham's comet\Nthis coming Thursday. -St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:26.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-It's a challenge!\N-A challenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:29.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:31.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,How's she gonna steal a comet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.19,0:07:36.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,There's no way...\NSo that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:40.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She's gonna steal\Nthe observatory's telescope!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.07,0:07:44.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's the only way to see\Nthe comet around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.75,0:07:49.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,My theory's definitely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:53.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Never mind.\NYou're dripping all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.33,0:07:57.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-But stealing it won't be easy.\N-I also agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.88,0:07:59.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:04.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She'll think of a way!\NI'll be ready for you, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.43,0:08:07.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,How can he be so sure\Nbased on no facts?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:11.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\NIt must be love, love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:18.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's a perfect night to present\Nthe comet to the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.59,0:08:21.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Ruby, take care of things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.41,0:08:28.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,No, Ruby! I have work to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.35,0:08:34.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, all right. Will you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:38.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Okay. But just this one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.71,0:08:45.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.56,0:08:52.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.07,0:08:55.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:09:00.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.65,0:09:21.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Meimi, hurry! Everyone will be\Nhere soon for choir practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.17,0:09:25.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I know. You and Ruby take care\Nof the other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.67,0:09:29.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The children will be happy for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.82,0:09:31.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You can count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:37.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:16.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wow. This certainly is\Na magnificent telescope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.46,0:10:22.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:26.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But why does she want a telescope?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:32.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-It will go smoothly tonight.\N-Especially without those pesky kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:37.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We can't let those kids ruin\Nsuch a great astronomical event.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.43,0:10:42.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-How's it going?\N-Everything's going smoothly, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.31,0:10:43.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.65,0:10:48.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr., is St. Tail really\Ncoming to steal this telescope?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:50.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm certain of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:55.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You've got the right idea\Nexcept for the last detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.24,0:10:58.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We'll leave you\Nto take care of St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.81,0:11:02.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We don't want our research\Nhampered by a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:04.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Of all the nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.36,0:11:09.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The comet passes once every 50 years.\NIt's just as important to children.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.37,0:11:13.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,They want to keep it for themselves.\NGod will never forgive this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,0:11:16.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:18.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:21.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:29.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Where did they come from?\N-Who did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.05,0:11:32.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.59,0:11:36.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-No, stop!\N-I was wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:42.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I know it's you, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.82,0:11:49.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,How's she gonna steal\Nthis huge thing anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:04.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.22,0:12:09.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,And now, I have some sad news\Nfor all of you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.10,0:12:13.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Today is Akio's last practice...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.28,0:12:17.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...since he will be leaving soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:23.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Take care.\N-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:26.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Too bad we couldn't see the comet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:29.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-It can't be helped.\N-See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:34.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Akio, I hope you never lose\Nyour bright outlook on life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:39.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-I won't! Goodbye, Mother Superior!\N-Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:48.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Mother Superior, where is Seira?\N-She's not out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.94,0:12:56.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but I am outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:13:01.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Though this is a little embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.19,0:13:09.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hello, children! These balloons\Nare for you from the snowman!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.91,0:13:17.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-This is a reward for being so good.\N-Gee, thanks, Mr. Snowman!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.82,0:13:21.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,There's one for everyone.\NHere you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:23.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wow! A snowman!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:28.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.35,0:13:30.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:43.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Akio. There's something\Non your balloon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.75,0:13:50.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Come to the observatory.\NI'll give you Graham's comet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:54.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Let's go!\N-Where are you kids going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.24,0:13:57.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We'll be right back, Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.85,0:14:04.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-What's this?\N-Get down here, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.79,0:14:07.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,If you don't, I'm going up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:12.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you for sure today\Nand unmask you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:22.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:26.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...show...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.91,0:14:29.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.67,0:14:40.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Sir! This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.47,0:14:44.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Look at the monitor!\N-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.15,0:14:48.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,A part of the comet has broken off...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:51.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...and is falling towards us\Nat great speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:53.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous! Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:59.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Why didn't you see this before?\N-I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.22,0:15:04.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,A part of the comet. That's\Nsomething like a meteor, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.06,0:15:06.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,No, very far from it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:11.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It could make a huge hole!\NWe may not be safe here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:15.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Let's get away!\N-Wait for me! Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.05,0:15:19.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's gone finally!\NNow's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.26,0:15:22.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! Don't you move from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.41,0:15:30.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you running away?\NA part of the comet is heading here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.25,0:15:32.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.79,0:15:36.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,So what? What could you\Nbe thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.96,0:15:39.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna arrest you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.95,0:15:47.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,My legs, I can't move them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.49,0:15:49.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Is there another reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:54.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Like what if you died, what's\Nthe most important thing you'd take?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.50,0:15:56.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Something important?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.54,0:15:59.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Yes. Do you have something?\N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.55,0:16:03.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I can't think of anything\Nuntil I arrest you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.06,0:16:23.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Meimi, no! Get ahold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.82,0:16:35.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. It was an act.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.36,0:16:41.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Nothing's falling to Earth.\NI rigged the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.94,0:16:43.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:46.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,One! Two! Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.87,0:16:56.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,COMET COLLIDES! THE LAST NIGHT\NON EARTH; THE END
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:16:58.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.81,0:17:15.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Why did you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:20.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I've recorded\Nthe correct data too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:24.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,And could you let in\Nthe children waiting outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:26.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.74,0:17:29.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.78,0:17:31.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:37.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Boy, that was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:40.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But he wouldn't have said it\Nlike that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:43.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...if he knew I was Meimi.\NI'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:52.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The children waiting outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.90,0:18:07.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:15.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wow, there it is! I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:18.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-The comet!\N-It really has a tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.69,0:18:20.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.17,0:18:26.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-I wonder when we'll see it again?\N-In 50 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.41,0:18:29.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Then let's all come here\Nagain to look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.78,0:18:30.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:34.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I just don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:38.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Why did St. Tail--?\NHey, what's this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.90,0:18:42.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.\NWe all prayed to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:46.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We asked Him to let us see the comet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.42,0:18:50.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:53.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,God.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.51,0:18:59.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Look, falling stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.36,0:19:07.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Did you ask God for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.93,0:19:10.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-No.\N-Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.94,0:19:13.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Because my wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.05,0:19:16.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...is for God.
